  <div class="hero-photo-overlay"></div>
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5 text-center">
    <p class="sl gp mb-4">Residential Roofing</p>
    <h1 class="font-display font-black tracking-tightest mb-5" style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(3rem,6vw,5rem);line-height:.92;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:#1A1A1A">
      RESIDENTIAL ROOFING<br/><span class="gt">BUILT FOR FLORIDA.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="color:#555555;font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.75">
      Your home deserves a roof that can handle Florida's intense heat, driving rain, and hurricane-force winds. Happy Roof installs high-performance roofing systems designed specifically for Tampa Bay's demanding climate - backed by a 15-year workmanship warranty.
    </p>
    <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-4" style="color:#777;font-size:.88rem;line-height:1.75">
      A full roof replacement in Tampa Bay typically costs between $8,000 and $25,000 for an average-sized home, depending on materials (asphalt shingles, metal, or tile) and roof complexity. Happy Roof LLC (FL License #CCC1337380) is an Owens Corning certified installer serving Hillsborough, Pinellas, and Pasco counties. All installations include up to a 15-year workmanship warranty plus manufacturer material warranties. Financing available. Call (813) 595-7663 for a free estimate.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

