        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">
          Choosing a roofing contractor is one of the biggest decisions a homeowner makes. At Happy Roof, we understand the weight of that decision - and we earn your trust with transparency, craftsmanship, and follow-through. We install premium Owens Corning and GAF roofing systems and meet the highest standards in the industry. Every project is led by a licensed foreman with years of Florida roofing experience, and all crews are fully vetted, licensed, and insured.
        </p>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">
          We hold Florida Roofing Contractor License #CCC1337380, carry full general liability and workers' compensation insurance, and pull all required permits for every job. When the work is done, we provide a 15-year workmanship warranty in writing - because a handshake isn't enough when it comes to protecting your home.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Owens Corning Installer</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">We install premium Owens Corning roofing systems with manufacturer warranties on all products.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">15-Year Workmanship Warranty</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">Every residential roof we install comes with a 15-year workmanship warranty - in writing, every time. No exceptions.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Vetted, Licensed Crews</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">Every crew member is fully licensed and insured. We oversee every project from start to finish.</p></div></div>
        </div>
