<!-- MATERIALS -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#F7F7F7">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <p class="sl gt mb-3">Roofing Materials</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.95;color:#1A1A1A;letter-spacing:-.01em">MATERIALS WE INSTALL</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

      <!-- Shingle -->
      <div class="scard p-8">
        <div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:rgba(230,168,23,.1);margin-bottom:1rem">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.35rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.75rem">Asphalt Shingles</h3>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:1rem">
          The most popular choice for Tampa Bay homes. We install Owens Corning Duration HDZ and UHDZ, Owens Corning Duration and Oakridge, and other premium architectural shingles rated for 130+ MPH winds. Shingle roofs offer excellent value, a wide range of color options, and proven performance in Florida's climate. Typical lifespan is 25 to 30 years with proper installation and ventilation.
        </p>
        <p style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:.85rem;color:#3B9FD9;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase">25–30 Year Lifespan</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Metal -->
      <div class="scard p-8">
        <div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:rgba(230,168,23,.1);margin-bottom:1rem">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M3 9h18M3 15h18M9 3v18M15 3v18"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.35rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.75rem">Metal Roofing</h3>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:1rem">
          Standing seam and exposed-fastener metal roofs are becoming the preferred choice for Florida homeowners who want maximum durability and energy efficiency. Metal reflects solar heat, reducing cooling costs by up to 25%. We install Gulf Coast Supply panels - GulfLok, GulfSeam, GulfSnap, GulfRib, and MegaLoc - all engineered for Florida's wind and rain. Metal roofs last 40 to 60 years and often qualify for insurance discounts.
        </p>
        <p style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:.85rem;color:#3B9FD9;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase">40–60 Year Lifespan</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Tile -->
      <div class="scard p-8">
        <div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:rgba(230,168,23,.1);margin-bottom:1rem">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.35rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.75rem">Tile Roofing</h3>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:1rem">
          Concrete and clay tile roofs deliver a classic Florida aesthetic with exceptional longevity. We install barrel tile, S-tile, and flat tile profiles from Verea and other top manufacturers. Tile is naturally fire-resistant, energy-efficient, and can withstand sustained high winds when properly installed. Tile roofs can last 50 years or more and add significant curb appeal and resale value to your home.
        </p>
        <p style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:.85rem;color:#3B9FD9;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase">50+ Year Lifespan</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- OUR PROCESS -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#FFFFFF">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <p class="sl gt mb-3">How It Works</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.95;color:#1A1A1A;letter-spacing:-.01em">OUR 4-STEP PROCESS</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Free Inspection & Estimate</h3>
          <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">We start with a thorough roof inspection - checking decking, underlayment, flashing, ventilation, and overall condition. You receive a detailed, written estimate with material options, timelines, and pricing. No pressure, no hidden fees, no obligation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Material Selection & Permits</h3>
          <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">Once you approve the scope, we help you select the ideal material and color for your home. We then pull all required permits with your local building department and order materials directly from the manufacturer. You pick the start date that works for you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Professional Installation</h3>
          <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">Our crew performs the full tear-off, inspects and repairs the decking as needed, installs new underlayment and flashing, and lays your new roofing system to manufacturer specifications. We protect your landscaping, driveway, and property throughout the process.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5">
        <div class="step-num">4</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Final Inspection & Warranty</h3>
          <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">After installation, we schedule the county inspection to verify code compliance. Once passed, we deliver your warranty documentation - including our 15-year workmanship warranty and the manufacturer material warranty. We follow up at 30 days and 1 year to make sure you're satisfied.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SERVICE AREA -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#F7F7F7">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
