      <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;max-width:700px;margin:0 auto">Happy Roof provides residential roofing services across Hillsborough, Pinellas, and Pasco counties. If your home is in Tampa Bay, we've got you covered.</p>
