      <div class="faq-answer">
        <div class="faq-answer-inner">Most residential shingle roof replacements in Tampa Bay take 1 to 3 days. Metal roofs typically take 3 to 5 days, and tile roofs may take 5 to 7 days depending on complexity and weather. Happy Roof handles all permits, county inspections, and job-site cleanup so you don't have to coordinate anything. We keep you updated throughout the process.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
